   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Sadly, both the add-ons that I've looked into require Django 1.4 or higher. 

I should make a new ticket to upgrade the whole OH project to the latest stable version of Django, which 
is currently at version 1.6.</pre>
   </td>
