  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>I attempted to integrate the django-allauth add-on without success: 
<a href="https://github.com/pennersr/django-allauth">https://github.com/pennersr/django-allauth</a> Why? Because one of the core Django modules called 
timezone in allauth requires Django 1.4, while the OH app runs on Django 1.3.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
