  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>GitHub would be the first of our login providers to use OAuth2, rather than 
OpenID, so there are going to be some implementation complexities here. But they 
should be fairly easily handled if we use some third-party Django add-on.</pre>
   </td>
